snippet.title: World of Warships Blitz Trailer
snippet.description:
Download World of Warships Blitz now for iOS and Android: https://bit.ly/2LwxK9l

World of Warships Blitz is a free-to-play mobile multiplayer action game by Wargaming and is based on the award-winning Navy Shooter on PC, World of Warships.
